data.description: Welcome to your opulent sanctuary! This magnificent residence boasts over 1,900 square feet of meticulously crafted living space.  Indulge in the embrace of 3 generously proportioned bedrooms, one of which can be designated as your exclusive guest wing, ensuring unrivaled privacy.  An open split floorplan, masterfully designed to safeguard your personal space.  Sitting on just under half-acre, contemplate the addition of a pool or an al fresco outdoor kitchen for hosting family gatherings and entertaining your cherished guests.  Located near local shopping and dining leisure. Come and make it yours today!  New roof-December 2023, Water Heater-2019, A/C-2018.
